==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: space-time
<hw>space-time</hw>, <pos>n.</pos> <def>the four-dimensional coordinate
system in which all physical objects of the known universe are located,
and in which all physical events occur; it consists of three spatial
dimensions and one time dimension; -- also called the
<altname>space-time continuum</altname>.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>PJC</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Space travel</ent>⟦br⟧
